          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "title_1": "Ground-Breaking Technology",
            "description_1": "<ul><li><strong>Vortex-Fusion Technology</strong> deeply cleanses by extracting impurities while infusing potent serums for instant results.</li><li><strong>Spiral dermabrasion tips</strong> enhance absorption and let you control exfoliation intensity.</li><li><strong>Personalize every treatment</strong> with adjustable chemical peels and targeted booster serums for specific skin concerns.</li><li>A <strong>smart, hands-free device</strong> with on-screen guidance keeps your focus where it matters — on your clients.</li></ul>",
