      "blocks": {
        "quote_REnyCi": {
          "type": "quote",
          "settings": {
            "quote": "<|Hydrafacial is a staple treatment in my practice|>. As a Facial Plastic and Reconstructive Surgeon, I use Hydrafacial as part of my surgical and procedural regimen. A series of treatments with the Hydrafacial system pre- and post- facial surgery can improve hydration, skin tone and texture, and help speed healing time, helping increase the clients' outcome and satisfaction. Introducing Hydrafacial into my clients' regimen is a great way to build practice revenue and generate repeat business.",
